## How It Works

```python
from ocp_agent import OCPAgent

agent = OCPAgent()

# Register an API with auth
await agent.register_api(
    'github',
    headers={'Authorization': 'Bearer your_token'}
)

# Use any tool
result = await agent.call_tool('reposGet', {
    'owner': 'opencontextprotocol',
    'repo': 'ocp-python'
})
```

